# ─── Anthropic (Claude AI) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ─── Google Places API ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Enable "Places API (New)" in Google Cloud Console, then create an API key.
# Restrict the key to the Places API and your domain for production.
# https://console.cloud.google.com/
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=AIza...

# ─── Notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Firebase config is hardcoded in app/lib/firebase.ts — Firebase web API keys
# are intentionally public (security is enforced by Firestore Rules, not the key).
#
# For local development: copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
#   cp .env.example .env.local
#
# For Vercel deployment: add these in Project Settings → Environment Variables.
